```json
{
  "application": "LSF",
  "details": {
    "software": {
      "LSF": "9.1.1",

      "OMP": ""
    },
    "resources": {
      "account": "optional",
      "group": "optional",
      "queue": "dev, dev_transfer or prod, with optional requirement",
      "timew": "wall time limit in [[hh:]mm:]ss format",
      "rmem": "memory per task in MB",
      "rcpu": "cpus per task",
      "procs": "number of MPI tasks",
      "nodes": "optional, number of nodes",
      "binding": "smt binding or not",
      "dirin": "initial directory",
      "envars": "comma-separated environment variables",
      "userid": "userid to run under",
      "when": "when to run, in yyyymmddhh[mm], +hh[mm], thh[mm], or Thh[mm] format",
      "pe_node": "cores per node"
    }
  }
}
```
